{{&lt; /example &gt;}}</p>
<h2>Row columns gutters</h2>
<p>Gutter classes can also be added to [row columns]({{&lt; docsref &quot;/layout/grid#row-columns&quot; &gt;}}). In the following example, we use responsive row columns and responsive gutter classes.</p>
